  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ターゲットは
&lt;Red&gt;ヴァルハラ村&lt;White&gt;を拠点とする
革命組織『シグルド』</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Our target is the rebel group
situated in &lt;Red&gt;Valhalla Village&lt;White&gt;, Sigurd.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そのリーダーである
『ブレイナー』の捕獲だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The mission is to capture
their leader, Brainer.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271172</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何か質問は？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Any questions?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271240</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>現在の戦況は？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's the current status?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>敵の魔科学兵器に
苦戦させられていますが、
現在、我が軍優勢です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The enemies' Magitech weapon has
made this a difficult battle. However,
we have the upper hand.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271440</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>街入り口をふさいでいる
バリケードが破られるのも
時間の問題です</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The entrance is completely barricaded,
but It's only a matter of time until
we break through.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271568</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦端が開いたら、
一気にたたみこむぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As soon as we're given the signal,
we will begin the assault.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271568</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;様、お願いします</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sir &lt;Cless&gt;, we'll rely on your support.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271624</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Roger!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ご報告します！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reporting, sir!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271768</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我が軍の先鋒が、
街南口のバリケードを
突破しました！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The barricade's been broken down!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271864</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_140_040_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし、全戦力を街へ向かわせろ！
総力戦だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right! Every unit march into
the city! All troops, move out!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
